My place is close to La Flor Bakery
, Starbucks, 24hour Rite Aid, Deli's, Laundry, Subway, 24hour supermarket near by.. My place is good for couples, solo adventurers, and business travelers.
name: 1 Bedroom apartment in Woodside, NY
review: Eliana is a great host. She is very attentive to any questions and/or concerns you may have. I had some trouble logging on to the internet due to being internet challenged, and she was there in a flash to help me out. The space is very convenient to mass transit and restaurants. I really enjoyed my stay.
